{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idef7471ee-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"100101"},"text":"§ 100101.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Promotion and regulation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef7471ef-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"In General","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary, acting through the Director of the National Park Service, shall promote and regulate the use of the National Park System by means and measures that conform to the fundamental purpose of the System units, which purpose is to conserve the scenery, natural and historic objects, and wild life in the System units and to provide for the enjoyment of the scenery, natural and historic objects, and wild life in such manner and by such means as will leave them unimpaired for the enjoyment of future generations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f0-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Declarations.—","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f1-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" 1970 ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"declarations","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Congress declares that—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f2-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/b/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the National Park System, which began with establishment of Yellowstone National Park in 1872, has since grown to include superlative natural, historic, and recreation areas in every major region of the United States and its territories and possessions;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f3-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/b/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" these areas, though distinct in character, are united through their interrelated purposes and resources into one National Park System as cumulative expressions of a single national heritage;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f4-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/b/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" individually and collectively, these areas derive increased national dignity and recognition of their superb environmental quality through their inclusion jointly with each other in one System preserved and managed for the benefit and inspiration of all the people of the United States; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f5-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/b/1/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" it is the purpose of this division to include all these areas in the System and to clarify the authorities applicable to the System.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f6-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db","identifier":"/us/usc/t54/s100101/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" 1978 ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"reaffirmation","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Congress reaffirms, declares, and directs that the promotion and regulation of the various System units shall be consistent with and founded in the purpose established by subsection (a), to the common benefit of all the people of the United States. The authorization of activities shall be construed and the protection, management, and administration of the System units shall be conducted in light of the high public value and integrity of the System and shall not be exercised in derogation of the values and purposes for which the System units have been established, except as directly and specifically provided by Congress.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idef7471f7-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/287/s3"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–287, § 3","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3096"},"text":"128 Stat. 3096","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idef7471f8-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"historicalAndRevision","id":"idef7471f9-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:table","attrib":{"width":"50%","id":"idef7471fa-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:colgroup","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:col","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:thead","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{"colspan":"3"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"Historical and Revision Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:i","attrib":{},"text":"Revised","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:i","attrib":{},"text":"Section","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:i","attrib":{},"text":"Source (U.S. Code)","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:th","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:i","attrib":{},"text":"Source (Statutes at Large)","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:tbody","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"100101(a)","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1","children":[],"tail":" (last sentence)."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1916-08-25/ch408/s1"},"text":"Aug. 25, 1916, ch. 408, § 1","children":[],"tail":" (last sentence), "},{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/39/535"},"text":"39 Stat. 535","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"100101(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1a–1"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1a–1","children":[],"tail":" (1st sentence)."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/383/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 91–383, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"Aug. 18, 1970","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/825"},"text":"84 Stat. 825","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/250/tI/s101/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–250, title I, § 101(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"Mar. 27, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/166"},"text":"92 Stat. 166","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"html:tr","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:span","attrib":{},"text":"100101(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"html:a","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1a–1"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1a–1","children":[],"tail":" (2d, last sentences)."}],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"html:td","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (a), the words “Secretary, acting through the Director of the National Park Service” are substituted for “service thus established” to reflect the transfer of functions of other officers, employees, and agencies of the Department of the Interior to the Secretary by sections 1 and 2 of Reorganization Plan No. 3 of 1950 (5 U.S.C. App.) while keeping the responsibility for promoting and regulating the use of the National Park System with the Director of the National Park Service.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In subsection (b)(1)(D), the words “this division” are substituted for “this Act” for clarity. The purpose of the Act of ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-08-18"},"text":"August 18, 1970","children":[],"tail":" (known as the National Park System General Authorities Act) ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/91/383"},"text":"Public Law 91–383","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/84/825"},"text":"84 Stat. 825","children":[],"tail":"), was to update and clarify the law with respect to the various units of the National Park System by enlarging the application of existing general statutes so that they apply uniformly to the administration of the various types of parklands within the national park system. See H. Rept. 91–1265 (91st Cong., 2d Sess.). However, section 2(b) of that Act, rather than being enacted as a new provision of law, amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1953-08-08/s2"},"text":"section 2 of the Act of August 8, 1953","children":[],"tail":" (ch. 384, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/67/496"},"text":"67 Stat. 496","children":[],"tail":"), and would not be included in the reference to “this Act” in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1970-08-18/s1"},"text":"section 1 of the Act of August 18, 1970","children":[],"tail":". The revised subsection translates the reference to “this Act” to carry out the intent of the Act of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1970-08-18"},"text":"August 18, 1970","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idef7471fb-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"shortTitleOfAmendment","id":"idef7471fc-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title of 2023 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/339/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–339, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2023-01-05"},"text":"Jan. 5, 2023","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/6158"},"text":"136 Stat. 6158","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/117/339/s1"},"text":"“This Act [enacting chapter 1201 of this title and provisions set out as notes under sections 120101 and 120102 of this title, amending provisions listed in tables and set out as a note under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t54/s120102"},"text":"section 120102 of this title","children":[],"tail":", and repealing provisions set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t54/s120102"},"text":"section 120102 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] may be cited as the ‘National Heritage Area Act’.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"shortTitleOfAmendment","id":"idef7471fd-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title of 2020 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/152/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–152, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2020-08-04"},"text":"Aug. 4, 2020","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/134/682"},"text":"134 Stat. 682","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/116/152/s1"},"text":"“This Act [enacting chapter 2004 of this title and amending sections 200302, 200303, and 200306 of this title] may be cited as the ‘Great American Outdoors Act’.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"shortTitleOfAmendment","id":"idef7471fe-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title of 2019 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/94/dP/tVII/s701"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–94, div. P, title VII, § 701","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2019-12-20"},"text":"Dec. 20, 2019","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/133/3195"},"text":"133 Stat. 3195","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/116/94/dP/tVII/s701"},"text":"“This title [enacting sections 308104 and 308105 of this title and amending ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t54/s308103"},"text":"section 308103 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] may be cited as the ‘Preserving America’s Battlefields Act’.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"shortTitleOfAmendment","id":"idef7471ff-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title of 2018 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/104/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–104, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-01-08"},"text":"Jan. 8, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/131/2260"},"text":"131 Stat. 2260","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/115/104/s1"},"text":"“This Act [enacting chapter 3084 of this title and provisions set out as a note under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t54/s308401"},"text":"section 308401 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] may be cited as the ‘African American Civil Rights Network Act of 2017’.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"shortTitleOfAmendment","id":"idef747200-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title of 2016 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/289/s1/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–289, § 1(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-16"},"text":"Dec. 16, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/1482"},"text":"130 Stat. 1482","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/114/289/s1/a"},"text":"“This Act [see Tables for classification] may be cited as the ‘National Park Service Centennial Act’.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/289/tII/s201"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–289, title II, § 201","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-16"},"text":"Dec. 16, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/1485"},"text":"130 Stat. 1485","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/114/289/tII/s201"},"text":"“This title [enacting ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t54/s101121"},"text":"section 101121 of this title","children":[],"tail":"] may be cited as the ‘National Park Foundation Endowment Act’.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/289/tVIII/s801"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–289, title VIII, § 801","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-16"},"text":"Dec. 16, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/1494"},"text":"130 Stat. 1494","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/114/289/tVIII/s801"},"text":"“This title [amending sections 302104 and 303102 of this title] may be cited as the ‘National Historic Preservation Amendments Act’.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idef747201-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Short Title of 2009 Act","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/11/s1/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–11, § 1(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-03-30"},"text":"Mar. 30, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/991"},"text":"123 Stat. 991","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/111/11/s1/a"},"text":"“This Act [see Tables for classification] may be cited as the ‘Omnibus Public Land Management Act of 2009’.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"mi